{"word":"ἐπιπόλαιος","slug":"ἐπιπόλαιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιπόλαιος</b></el> <el>(ἐπιπόλαιος, ον) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>on the surface, superficial</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b>:— <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>superficial, common-place</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>prominent</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἐπιπολή'><el>ἐπιπολή</el></a>\n"}]}